title: Сверхъестественные
overview: Our country is a huge market for paid magic services. Neither marriages nor business deals are concluded without consulting an astrologer or psychic. Hundreds of witchcraft ads are published in newspapers, and the Internet is full of websites of hereditary shamans and fortune tellers. But how does the magic industry actually work, where quite real, and at the same time, considerable money is involved?We will show the whole truth about otherworldly trade! The famous mentalist Lior Suchard and a psychologist-reporter with 15 years of experience Angela Boskis will reveal the secrets of a profitable business. How much does a miracle cost in modern packaging? What is the basis - the desire to help or the thirst for profit? How to distinguish a real psychic from a skilled charlatan? And do shamans have quality certificates?Lior Suchard and Angela Boskis will find real, practicing magicians and test their skills in practice. No tricks or special effects!To believe or not to believe is up to you.
